00:10:35.810 --> 00:10:38.950
So the reason it does not
show up with an icon is

00:10:38.950 --> 00:10:40.950
because there is one
other rule to be aware of.

00:10:40.950 --> 00:10:42.050
Let me say it a little differently.

00:10:42.050 --> 00:10:43.690
There is no error.

00:10:43.690 --> 00:10:47.040
Same color; but this larger
