default, that blue box

00:33:09.150 --> 00:33:12.120
with the light gray glow
is my focus indication,

00:33:12.120 --> 00:33:14.600
that would fail this requirement.

00:33:14.600 --> 00:33:16.870
Because the difference
between these two,

00:33:16.870 --> 00:33:18.990
