00:46:51.370 --> 00:46:54.900
Yes, so one thing Beatrice
asked, it really is

00:46:54.900 --> 00:46:57.710
that the test is really
foreground and background of text,

00:46:57.710 --> 00:46:58.750
and some kind of skipping around.

00:46:58.750 --> 00:47:01.480
The question is: Do we need
to perform contrast tests

00:47:01.480 --> 00:47:04.860
